name: COVID19ICD10CMValueSetForDementia
title: COVID19 ICD10CM Value Set for Dementia
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to dementia and is listed as a neurologic disorder on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes vascular, alzheimers, substance associated dementia (e.g. Alcohol dependence with alcohol-induced persisting dementia), Creutzfeld-Jacob disease, etc.),(Exclusion Criteria: )
